WEBVTT

01:52:26.291 --> 01:52:29.959
"You let that poor boy
die in order to get bait,
you monster!"

01:52:31.595 --> 01:52:32.995
The cook got furious.

01:52:32.997 --> 01:52:35.298
He started towards her
with his fist raised...

01:52:35.300 --> 01:52:38.034
and Mother slapped him hard,
right across the face.
